thread.title: Jerome Dingle
thread.title_full: PRO Import Tuners.com reviewed by Jerome Dingle

author: Jerome Dingle
title: Jerome Dingle
text: I ordered a roof spoiler which I have been searching for since 2014. At the time the warehouse was out of the spoiler so they had to order one. I was surprised to receive a call from an ACTUAL PERSON to explain what was going on and why I was delayed. In this day and age when its an email or automated call...IT WAS GREAT TO ACTUALLY TALK TO A REAL PERSON!!!! That I truly appreciate! I will be looking at ordering what ever parts I desire from them and only go elsewhere if they don't have what I want. I'd highly recommend them GREAT SERVICE!!!
